data.description: Dramatic lakefront home with pool in guard gated community with 24 hour security. Light and bright with cathedral ceilings.  4 bedrooms plus loft.  Master suite is on the first floor with a sitting room which opens out to pool/patio and lake. Bath with smart toilet, heated towel racks, waterfall shower and double sinks has been recently updated.  Second level encompasses three additional bedrooms and 2 baths which have also been recently updated plus a loft.  Formal dining room, plus a large kitchen with additional breakfast area. Great room opens to pool/patio and lake.  Numerous updates in this beautiful home with a new front door in 2020, new sliding doors and bathrooms in 2019. San Remo has a beautiful community pool, clubhouse, gym and playground. Location and value!
